---
title: Cheesy Corn Fritters & Potato Fries with Apple Salad & Herby Mayo
description: These gloriously bright fritters are both crunchy and sweet and are set off perfectly by an A-team of dill-parsley mayo, golden fries and a crunchy apple salad. If you fancy it, sprinkle some toasted almonds over the salad for ultimate crunch!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
